+# Phase 2.22 — Route Incident RCA Experiment Harness
+
+## Цель
+Добавить A/B routing buckets, exposure logging и winner selection для нового `route incident RCA` routing-контура.
+
+## Потоки
+- input: `stream:ml:operator_routing_incident_rca_route_rca_requests_routed`
+- experimented: `stream:ml:operator_routing_incident_route_rca_requests_experimented`
+- exposures: `stream:ml:operator_routing_incident_route_rca_exposures`
+- winner decisions: `stream:ml:operator_routing_incident_route_rca_experiment_winner_decisions`
+- audit: `stream:ml:operator_routing_incident_route_rca_experiment_audit`
+
+## Safe start
+```bash
+export ML_OPERATOR_ROUTING_INCIDENT_ROUTE_RCA_EXPERIMENT_ENABLE=1
+export ML_OPERATOR_ROUTING_INCIDENT_ROUTE_RCA_EXPERIMENT_ID=route_incident_rca_ab_v1
+export ML_OPERATOR_ROUTING_INCIDENT_ROUTE_RCA_EXPERIMENT_MIN_SAMPLE=8
+export ML_OPERATOR_ROUTING_INCIDENT_ROUTE_RCA_EXPERIMENT_WINDOW_MIN=1440
+```
+
+## Smoke checks
+```bash
+redis-cli XREVRANGE stream:ml:operator_routing_incident_route_rca_requests_experimented + - COUNT 5
+redis-cli XREVRANGE stream:ml:operator_routing_incident_route_rca_exposures + - COUNT 5
+redis-cli XREVRANGE stream:ml:operator_routing_incident_route_rca_experiment_winner_decisions + - COUNT 5
+redis-cli XREVRANGE stream:ml:operator_routing_incident_route_rca_experiment_audit + - COUNT 10
+curl -s localhost:9907/metrics | grep '^ml_operator_routing_incident_route_rca_experiment_'
+curl -s localhost:9908/metrics | grep '^ml_operator_routing_incident_route_rca_experiment_'
+```
+
+## Notes
+- scope только `scanner_infra`
+- hot path не затронут
+- winner decision пока advisory-only
